  <entry>
    <title>使用Hexo搭建自己的blog</title>
    <link href="/2022/11/21/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84blog/"/>
    <url>/2022/11/21/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84blog/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="预备知识（必备）"><a href="#预备知识（必备）" class="headerlink" title="预备知识（必备）"></a>预备知识（必备）</h2><h3 id="Node（必须）"><a href="#Node（必须）" class="headerlink" title="Node（必须）"></a>Node（必须）</h3><p>安装 node，版本为 14 以上,且成功添加环境变量<br>成功标志</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">node -v<br>v14.15.3<br><br>npm -v<br>6.14.9<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Git（必须）"><a href="#Git（必须）" class="headerlink" title="Git（必须）"></a>Git（必须）</h3><p>配置用户名、邮箱、生成 SSH 密钥</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">git config --global user.name &quot;lbwnb&quot;<br>git config --global user.email &quot;lbwnb@qq.com&quot;<br>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;lbwnb@qq.com&quot;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>成功标志</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">git config user.name<br>lbwnb<br><br>git config user.email<br>lbwnb@qq.com<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>且 C:&#x2F;Users&#x2F;hcx&#x2F;.ssh 文件夹下生成 id_rsa.pub 文件</p><p>且将 id_rsa.pub 内容添加到 <a href="https://github.com/settings/keys">github.com</a></p><h3 id="Vscode（非必须）"><a href="#Vscode（非必须）" class="headerlink" title="Vscode（非必须）"></a>Vscode（非必须）</h3><p>下载安装</p><h2 id="使用-github-生成一个个人网站"><a href="#使用-github-生成一个个人网站" class="headerlink" title="使用 github 生成一个个人网站"></a>使用 github 生成一个个人网站</h2><h3 id="创建仓库"><a href="#创建仓库" class="headerlink" title="创建仓库"></a>创建仓库</h3><p>进入<a href="https://github.com/new">创建</a>仓库页面</p><p>填写仓库名，格式必须为<code>&lt;用户名&gt;.github.io</code>，然后点击<code>Create repository</code></p><img src="/2022/11/21/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84blog/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93.png" class="" title="使用github创建个人网站"><p>完成后访问<code>&lt;用户名&gt;.github.io</code>就是我们的主页</p><h3 id="创建-Hexo-项目"><a href="#创建-Hexo-项目" class="headerlink" title="创建 Hexo 项目"></a>创建 Hexo 项目</h3><p>安装 hexo-cli 脚手架，帮你创建 hexo 项目</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">npm install -g hexo-cli<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>成功标志</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">hexo -v<br>// 输出<br>INFO  Validating config<br>hexo: 6.3.0<br>hexo-cli: 4.3.0<br>os: win32 10.0.19045<br>node: 14.15.3<br>v8: 8.4.371.19-node.17<br>uv: 1.40.0<br>zlib: 1.2.11<br>brotli: 1.0.9<br>ares: 1.16.1<br>modules: 83<br>nghttp2: 1.41.0<br>napi: 7<br>llhttp: 2.1.3<br>openssl: 1.1.1g<br>cldr: 37.0<br>icu: 67.1<br>tz: 2020a<br>unicode: 13.0<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>生成 hexo 项目</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">hexo init my-blog<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开 vscode，文件 -&gt; 打开文件夹</p><img src="/2022/11/21/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84blog/vscode%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C.png" class="" title="使用github创建个人网站"><p><code>Ctrl + ~</code>打开终端</p><img src="/2022/11/21/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84blog/vscode%E7%BB%88%E7%AB%AF.png" class="" title="使用github创建个人网站"><p>执行</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">npm install<br><br>npm server<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接下来到浏览器输入<a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000/</a>，可看到页面</p><h3 id="配置主题"><a href="#配置主题" class="headerlink" title="配置主题"></a>配置主题</h3><p>个人觉得<a href="https://hexo.io/themes/">官网主题</a>不好看，故更换</p><p>自行配置</p><h4 id="NexT-主题"><a href="#NexT-主题" class="headerlink" title="NexT 主题"></a>NexT 主题</h4><p>点击 vscode 终端右上角的<code>+</code>号，打开另外一个终端</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs git">git clone https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next themes/next<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="Fluid-主题"><a href="#Fluid-主题" class="headerlink" title="Fluid 主题"></a>Fluid 主题</h4><p>下载 <a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid/releases">最新 release 版本</a> 解压到 themes 目录，并将解压出的文件夹重命名为 fluid</p><p>在根目录的<code>_config.yml</code>指定主题</p><figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs avrasm"><span class="hljs-symbol">theme:</span> fluid  <span class="hljs-meta"># 指定主题</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">language:</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">zh</span>-CN  <span class="hljs-meta"># 指定语言，会影响主题显示的语言，按需修改</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="创建文章"><a href="#创建文章" class="headerlink" title="创建文章"></a>创建文章</h2><h3 id="创建「关于页」"><a href="#创建「关于页」" class="headerlink" title="创建「关于页」"></a>创建「关于页」</h3><p>命令</p><figure class="highlight haxe"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs haxe">hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-type">page</span> about<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>关于页的配置</p><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dts"><span class="hljs-meta">#---------------------------</span><br><span class="hljs-meta"># 关于页</span><br><span class="hljs-meta"># About Page</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#---------------------------</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">about:</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  enable:</span> true<br><span class="hljs-symbol">  banner_img:</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">/img/</span>default.png <span class="hljs-comment">// 大背景图</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  banner_img_height:</span> <span class="hljs-number">60</span> <span class="hljs-comment">// 大背景图高度</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  banner_mask_alpha:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0.3</span> <span class="hljs-comment">// 大背景图蒙板透明度</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  avatar:</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">/img/</span>avatar.jpg <span class="hljs-comment">// 头像</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;H&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-comment">// 昵称</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  intro:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;一个没有故事的白日梦想家 &amp; 不怎么勤劳的搬运工&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-comment">// 简介</span><br>  <span class="hljs-meta"># 更多图标可从 https:<span class="hljs-comment">//hexo.fluid-dev.com/docs/icon/ 查找，`class` 代表图标的 css class，添加 `qrcode` 后，图标不再是链接而是悬浮二维码</span></span><br>  <span class="hljs-meta"># More icons can be found from https:<span class="hljs-comment">//hexo.fluid-dev.com/docs/en/icon/  `class` is the css class of the icon. If adding `qrcode`, The icon is no longer a link, but a hovering QR code</span></span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  icons:</span><br>    - <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span> class: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;iconfont icon-github-fill&quot;</span>, link: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;https://github.com&quot;</span>, tip: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;GitHub&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><br>    - <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span> class: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;iconfont icon-douban-fill&quot;</span>, link: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;https://douban.com&quot;</span>, tip: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;豆瓣&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><br>    - <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span> class: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;iconfont icon-wechat-fill&quot;</span>, qrcode: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;/img/wechat.jpg&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span> <span class="hljs-comment">// 微信二维码</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="创建「分类页」"><a href="#创建「分类页」" class="headerlink" title="创建「分类页」"></a>创建「分类页」</h3><p>命令</p><figure class="highlight haxe"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs haxe">hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-type">page</span> categories<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>找到<code>source/categories/index.md</code>文件，添加<code>type: &quot;categories&quot;</code></p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">title:</span> <span class="hljs-string">categories</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">date:</span> <span class="hljs-number">2022-11-21 15:30:47</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;categories&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后去具体文章中配置</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">title:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Hello</span> <span class="hljs-string">World</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">categories:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Hexo教程&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">tags:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Hexo&quot;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Fluid&quot;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;教程&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="创建「标签页」"><a href="#创建「标签页」" class="headerlink" title="创建「标签页」"></a>创建「标签页」</h3><p>命令</p><figure class="highlight haxe"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs haxe">hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-type">page</span> tags<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>找到<code>source/tags/index.md</code>文件，添加<code>type: &quot;tags&quot;</code></p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">title:</span> <span class="hljs-string">tags</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">date:</span> <span class="hljs-number">2022-11-21 15:30:47</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后去具体文章中配置</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">title:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Hello</span> <span class="hljs-string">World</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">categories:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Hexo教程&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">tags:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Hexo&quot;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Fluid&quot;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;教程&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="创建自己的文章"><a href="#创建自己的文章" class="headerlink" title="创建自己的文章"></a>创建自己的文章</h3><p>修改根目录<code>_config.yml</code>，将<code>post_asset_folder</code>改为<code>true</code>，每次新建文章时会自动为文章生成一个同名文件夹，用于存放图片等资源文件</p><p>命令</p><figure class="highlight haxe"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs haxe">hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-type">post</span> 测试文章<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="其他设置"><a href="#其他设置" class="headerlink" title="其他设置"></a>其他设置</h2><h3 id="各种文字信息"><a href="#各种文字信息" class="headerlink" title="各种文字信息"></a>各种文字信息</h3><p>浏览器 tab 名：<br>修改根目录下 <code>_config.yml</code> 中的 title 字段</p><p>左上角博客标题：<br>修改主题目录<code>themes\fluid</code>下 <code>_config.yml</code> 中的 navbar -&gt; blog_title 字段</p><p>主页正中间的文字：<br>修改主题目录<code>themes\fluid</code>下 <code>_config.yml</code> 中的 slogan -&gt; text 字段</p><h3 id="阅读量统计"><a href="#阅读量统计" class="headerlink" title="阅读量统计"></a>阅读量统计</h3><p>注册<a href="https://console.leancloud.cn/">LeanCloud</a>，进行邮箱、实名认证。</p><p>创建应用，选择免费配置即可</p><p>进入该应用的 <code>设置</code> -&gt; <code>应用凭证</code>，找到 <code>AppID</code> 、 <code>AppKey</code> 和 <code>RestApi服务器地址</code>，记录下来后面配置要用</p><img src="/2022/11/21/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84blog/leancloud.png" class="" title="使用github创建个人网站"><p>打开主题目录 <code>themes\fluid</code>下的 <code>_config.yml</code> 文件</p><p>修改 <code>web_analytics</code> -&gt; <code>enable: true</code></p><p>修改 <code>web_analytics</code> -&gt; <code>leancloud</code>，填写 AppID 等</p><p>搜索 <code>浏览量计数</code>，修改 <code>views</code> -&gt; <code>enable: true</code> &amp; <code>source: &quot;leancloud&quot;</code>，展示标题下的 <code>阅读次数</code></p><p>搜索 <code>PV、UV</code>，修改 <code>statistics</code> -&gt; <code>enable: true</code> &amp; <code>source: &quot;leancloud&quot;</code>，展示底部的 <code>总访问量</code> 和 <code>总访问量</code></p><img src="/2022/11/21/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84blog/learncloud%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE.png" class=""><h3 id="文章评论"><a href="#文章评论" class="headerlink" title="文章评论"></a>文章评论</h3><p>搜索 <code>valine</code>，找到 valine 配置项，填写 LeanCloud 的 AppID 等</p><p>搜索 <code>评论插件</code>，修改 <code>comments</code> -&gt; <code>enable: true</code> &amp; <code>type: valine</code></p><h2 id="发布"><a href="#发布" class="headerlink" title="发布"></a>发布</h2><h3 id="生成-Token"><a href="#生成-Token" class="headerlink" title="生成 Token"></a>生成 Token</h3><p>去 <a href="https://github.com/settings/tokens">github</a> 配置一个 token，全部默认选项，直接确定</p><h3 id="配置-Token"><a href="#配置-Token" class="headerlink" title="配置 Token"></a>配置 Token</h3><p>修改根目录下的 <code>_config.yml</code>，配置 GitHub 相关信息</p><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dts"><span class="hljs-symbol">deploy:</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  type:</span> git<br><span class="hljs-symbol">  repo:</span> git@github.com:hcx777/hcx777.github.io.git <span class="hljs-comment">// 此处选择 SSH 地址</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  branch:</span> main<br><span class="hljs-symbol">  token:</span> ghp_3KakcaPHerunNRy12312321321<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="配置命令"><a href="#配置命令" class="headerlink" title="配置命令"></a>配置命令</h3><p>配置如图，在终端执行 <code>npm + 命令</code></p><img src="/2022/11/21/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84blog/script.png" class="" title="使用github创建个人网站"><h3 id="打包发布"><a href="#打包发布" class="headerlink" title="打包发布"></a>打包发布</h3><figure class="highlight coffeescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs coffeescript"><span class="hljs-built_in">npm</span> deploy<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
